WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

00:13.260 --> 00:16.130
Hold your soul and body as one.

00:16.500 --> 00:18.000
First, observe Heaven.

00:18.000 --> 00:19.630
[Wu Gen]

00:19.630 --> 00:21.970
[Xiaobangchui]
Second, observe Earth.

00:23.020 --> 00:25.360
Third, observe people.

00:26.500 --> 00:28.160
The artwork is so bad.

00:28.540 --> 00:29.730
And they charged me 30 wen?

00:30.000 --> 00:30.750
Save me!

00:30.750 --> 00:31.360
Darn it.

00:31.630 --> 00:32.410
Master, slow down.

00:32.430 --> 00:33.640
- Master! - Master!

00:33.860 --> 00:34.730
Stay back!

00:35.700 --> 00:39.570
The demon hiding in your estate is powerful

00:39.950 --> 00:44.290
and very cunning. It's quite troublesome.

00:46.230 --> 00:50.120
Xiaobangchui, have you found out what kind of demon it is?

00:53.060 --> 00:54.250
I've figured it out, Master.

00:55.660 --> 00:56.570
This trip is dangerous.

00:58.380 --> 01:00.810
This demon is called Tanmei. It feeds on human life force.

01:01.100 --> 01:02.320
At best, it brings illness and misfortune.

01:02.550 --> 01:05.040
At worst, you'll see blood within ten days.

01:05.060 --> 01:06.320
Master, it's a bad omen!

01:07.310 --> 01:10.810
Master, please save my family!

01:10.830 --> 01:12.370
Please save me.

01:12.390 --> 01:14.250
Sir, please rise.

01:15.110 --> 01:17.320
I'll do my best.

01:18.220 --> 01:19.370
Master, no!

01:19.940 --> 01:21.970
Defeating this great demon will cost you 30 years of your life.

01:21.990 --> 01:22.920
It'll damage your very core.

01:22.940 --> 01:25.120
Only a thousand-year Lingzhi can restore it, Master.

01:25.140 --> 01:25.680
Well...

01:27.060 --> 01:29.810
Master, here's the money for the Ganoderma lucidum.

01:32.670 --> 01:33.650
Everyone, watch out!

01:38.860 --> 01:42.650
Heaven and earth, source of all energy.

01:42.830 --> 01:45.810
By this talisman, reveal yourself, demon!

01:45.830 --> 01:46.730
Go!

01:53.700 --> 01:55.730
Demon! There it is!

01:56.910 --> 01:58.530
A demon! Look, right there!

01:58.550 --> 01:59.200
Right there!

02:01.830 --> 02:03.970
Take the money to solve their problem. Be quick.

02:04.140 --> 02:05.320
Me again?

02:06.140 --> 02:07.370
Who else, me?

02:10.990 --> 02:12.050
Master, hold the fort here.

02:12.230 --> 02:13.280
I'll go handle the demon.

02:16.620 --> 02:17.970
- Such skill! - Indeed.

02:34.280 --> 02:35.520
[Ancestral Hall]

02:37.620 --> 02:38.970
By the power of the spirits, break!

03:03.600 --> 03:05.080
[Lei Xiuyuan]

03:27.180 --> 03:27.930
Who are you?

03:27.950 --> 03:28.930
- You're not from Longming Sanctuary. - You are...?

03:33.140 --> 03:33.720
No, wait.

03:34.670 --> 03:35.770
Whether you're human or a demon,

03:36.110 --> 03:37.090
can we talk this out?

03:37.670 --> 03:39.650
Just find another place to stay.

03:39.670 --> 03:41.280
Stop bothering the owners of this house.

03:48.830 --> 03:49.840
What a fierce demon.

03:51.620 --> 03:53.120
Bind the soul and expel evil, seal!

04:04.950 --> 04:07.330
Sir, the demon you're looking for is right here.

04:07.580 --> 04:10.370
I... I'm just passing by.

04:10.550 --> 04:11.330
You menace!

04:11.830 --> 04:12.930
You're the menace here!

04:28.420 --> 04:29.160
Go die somewhere else!

04:32.260 --> 04:33.400
What's wrong with you?

05:20.590 --> 05:23.600
Master, I'll see you in the next life!

05:42.910 --> 05:46.210
Senior Brother, you finally showed up.

06:42.280 --> 06:43.580
[The Eternal Fragrance]

06:43.580 --> 06:47.880
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

06:47.880 --> 06:50.880
[Episode 1]

06:50.880 --> 06:54.120
[Qingqiu]

07:05.380 --> 07:06.010
Go away.

07:08.670 --> 07:09.280
Master!

07:10.380 --> 07:11.770
Master! Master?

07:12.820 --> 07:13.600
Master!

07:23.710 --> 07:24.690
You old geezer!

07:24.820 --> 07:26.280
You always bail whenever there's trouble.

07:26.380 --> 07:27.570
What kind of master does that?

07:28.620 --> 07:31.600
You are so clever.

07:31.790 --> 07:34.450
You'll always find a way out of trouble.

07:35.790 --> 07:36.360
Oh,

07:38.030 --> 07:38.770
I got this for you.

07:39.990 --> 07:41.040
You're wasting money again!

07:41.470 --> 07:43.210
Is it easy for us to make money

07:43.230 --> 07:44.600
by pulling these scams?

07:44.620 --> 07:45.770
And you keep buying stuff!

07:46.500 --> 07:47.920
Open it up.

07:51.110 --> 07:52.010
Do you like it?

07:53.820 --> 07:55.600
Are you still

07:55.670 --> 07:56.650
my stingy master

07:56.790 --> 07:58.600
who wouldn't even buy me candy?

07:59.940 --> 08:00.970
What are you talking about?

08:01.300 --> 08:02.770
If you like it, wear it.

08:02.790 --> 08:04.800
If not, I'll return it!

08:10.910 --> 08:11.600
Xiaobangchui!

08:13.110 --> 08:14.650
You're a girl. Don't you know

08:14.670 --> 08:16.650
you're supposed to change in your own room?

08:18.110 --> 08:20.480
Of course, it's not all your fault.

08:20.710 --> 08:21.650
I'm to blame too.

08:21.820 --> 08:24.090
I've always treated you like your senior brother.

08:24.300 --> 08:26.400
I've practically raised you like a boy.

08:28.620 --> 08:30.240
You keep talking about him.

08:30.790 --> 08:31.530
But I've never seen him

08:31.550 --> 08:33.090
since I can remember.

08:34.060 --> 08:35.480
Did you just make him up?

08:36.020 --> 08:38.120
Have I ever lied to you?

08:38.190 --> 08:39.450
Your senior brother

08:39.900 --> 08:42.570
is smarter than you. Extremely talented.

08:42.950 --> 08:44.240
By the time he was in his teens,

08:44.260 --> 08:46.120
I had nothing left to teach him.

08:46.140 --> 08:46.840
Eventually,

08:46.990 --> 08:49.240
he got into Chufeng Academy on his own.

08:49.990 --> 08:51.600
Then keep thinking about him.

08:52.830 --> 08:54.520
I'm going to change into my new clothes.

08:54.540 --> 08:56.290
Fine. Then get the radish stew going.

08:56.310 --> 08:57.290
I'm hungry.

08:58.500 --> 09:01.050
You had money but didn't buy meat?

09:01.070 --> 09:02.120
You're so cheap!

09:02.740 --> 09:04.410
Add more salt. I like it salty.

09:04.430 --> 09:05.840
Got it.

09:06.540 --> 09:07.290
Xiaobangchui.

09:08.260 --> 09:10.120
What now?

09:16.900 --> 09:19.720
Nothing. Just be careful when you cook.

09:20.470 --> 09:21.570
Don't get your new clothes dirty.

09:21.830 --> 09:23.290
I'm not as unreliable as you.

09:37.620 --> 09:42.000
Xiuyuan, put me down. Just leave me behind.

09:42.950 --> 09:43.930
Don't talk nonsense.

09:44.500 --> 09:45.600
[Lu Shanhua]
We said

09:45.950 --> 09:47.120
we'd find a place where no one knows us.

09:47.430 --> 09:48.690
We can farm or fish.

09:49.140 --> 09:50.520
Just never live a life on the run again.

09:51.740 --> 09:52.570
You can't leave me.

10:03.600 --> 10:06.880
[Young Lei Xiuyuan]

10:27.310 --> 10:28.690
My spirit meridians are completely broken.

10:29.540 --> 10:30.810
I don't have much time left.

10:31.830 --> 10:33.050
I can't drag you down.

10:34.590 --> 10:36.290
Isn't that what family do? Drag each other down?

10:37.500 --> 10:38.480
When Gaolu fell,

10:39.190 --> 10:40.090
our whole family

10:40.430 --> 10:42.090
went down together.

10:43.310 --> 10:45.210
We made it out and survived this long

10:45.620 --> 10:47.210
because heaven wants us to live.

10:52.590 --> 10:54.090
Soup's ready!

10:56.620 --> 10:58.120
Why are you using an evasion spell at home?

10:58.140 --> 10:59.050
Are you hiding money or something?

11:02.310 --> 11:02.930
Master?

11:04.230 --> 11:04.930
Master?

11:08.500 --> 11:09.600
Where's Master?

11:10.380 --> 11:11.050
Master?

11:14.740 --> 11:15.480
Master!

11:16.500 --> 11:17.520
Master!

11:30.310 --> 11:31.170
Xiaobangchui,

11:31.470 --> 11:33.330
I must leave for something urgent.

11:33.500 --> 11:34.480
Can't take you with me.

11:35.260 --> 11:37.450
Go to Chufeng Academy to find your senior brother.

11:37.860 --> 11:39.840
I've included his portrait with the letter.

11:40.110 --> 11:41.690
He seems quite capable.

11:41.710 --> 11:42.760
You can't go wrong with him.

11:50.380 --> 11:52.170
Why suddenly ask me to find some senior brother?

11:53.950 --> 11:55.000
You didn't even take your bag?

12:04.070 --> 12:05.520
He left all the money to me?

12:08.350 --> 12:09.090
Master.

12:17.540 --> 12:18.290
Master!

12:19.990 --> 12:21.000
Master!

12:24.830 --> 12:26.170
Master!

12:43.350 --> 12:44.170
You old geezer!

12:45.740 --> 12:47.000
You abandoned me.

12:47.620 --> 12:49.330
I can't live on my own!

12:52.230 --> 12:53.410
I might as well die!

13:02.430 --> 13:06.290
Help, Master! I'm dying!

13:10.500 --> 13:12.000
That heartless old geezer!

13:26.950 --> 13:27.570
Silly me.

13:28.110 --> 13:30.000
That old man always fears death. He won't come save me.

13:33.310 --> 13:34.000
That's not right.

13:35.310 --> 13:36.170
If he's scared of dying,

13:36.710 --> 13:38.570
he should hide with more money.

13:39.620 --> 13:40.360
Unless...

13:41.660 --> 13:43.720
Unless he ran into some life-threatening danger

13:44.020 --> 13:45.170
and knew he probably wouldn't make it?

13:45.190 --> 13:46.120
That's why he left me behind?

13:47.620 --> 13:49.720
Master... Master's in trouble.

14:08.350 --> 14:08.930
Demon.

14:09.280 --> 14:10.320
[Nine-Tailed Fox, Riyan]

14:11.110 --> 14:11.810
A fox spirit!

14:37.620 --> 14:38.450
You're hurt?

14:57.450 --> 14:58.880
[Immortal Dongyang, Wuyue Court]

15:09.470 --> 15:10.720
[Zhenyunzi, Xingzheng Hall]
Why is there a mortal in Qingqiu?

15:12.730 --> 15:13.900
[Lady Longjing, Huolian Abbey]

15:13.900 --> 15:14.880
It's a child.

15:15.500 --> 15:16.450
Who are you?

15:17.350 --> 15:18.840
Why are you alone in this deep forest?

15:30.540 --> 15:31.520
Whose blood is this?

15:37.900 --> 15:38.810
Mine. I got hurt.

15:42.430 --> 15:44.330
Tell me, what did you see?

15:47.110 --> 15:49.290
So cold. He's casting a spell on me.

15:55.230 --> 15:55.930
Mr. Zhenyun,

15:56.500 --> 15:57.880
she's just an ordinary person.

15:58.350 --> 16:00.170
She can't handle your verbal command spell.

16:04.380 --> 16:05.120
Don't be scared.

16:05.860 --> 16:06.930
Where's your family?

16:07.780 --> 16:09.880
Why did you come into the mountains alone?

16:10.070 --> 16:12.970
I... I live up in the mountains with my master.

16:13.230 --> 16:14.410
But my master disappeared.

16:14.830 --> 16:15.930
I've been looking for him everywhere.

16:15.950 --> 16:18.480
I don't know... where he is.

16:20.500 --> 16:21.410
Who's your master?

16:23.070 --> 16:24.570
Wu... Wu Gen.

16:26.260 --> 16:27.360
Wu Gen?

16:32.380 --> 16:34.880
There are countless reclusive cultivators in this world.

16:37.190 --> 16:39.410
This girl has a pure aura.

16:40.350 --> 16:42.970
She must be a good person.

16:47.660 --> 16:49.720
Don't be afraid, child.

16:50.190 --> 16:53.050
Did you see a white-furred fox spirit

16:53.070 --> 16:54.090
pass by just now?

17:01.070 --> 17:01.760
Where did it go?

17:02.230 --> 17:02.880
There!

17:03.310 --> 17:04.840
A white shadow

17:04.860 --> 17:05.840
just flew that way.

17:34.540 --> 17:36.450
Tell me, where's the fox?

17:36.950 --> 17:38.080
I don't know what you're talking about!

17:38.100 --> 17:38.890
Let me go!

17:39.780 --> 17:40.800
What about Riyan?

17:41.390 --> 17:43.080
What Riyan? I don't know anything about that!

17:43.100 --> 17:45.480
I don't know who Riyan is!

17:45.950 --> 17:46.480
Speak!

17:47.950 --> 17:48.760
If you kill me,

17:49.150 --> 17:50.370
you'll never find out!

17:50.950 --> 17:51.690
Speak!

18:01.670 --> 18:03.780
This girl is looking for her family.

18:04.430 --> 18:07.060
Please spare her.

18:09.230 --> 18:10.100
Please, have mercy.

18:10.470 --> 18:11.320
Let me go.

18:29.740 --> 18:32.800
Sir, your vital energy was already unstable.

18:33.260 --> 18:35.080
And now you've been badly wounded by the fox.

18:35.670 --> 18:37.450
If you don't retreat to heal soon,

18:37.780 --> 18:40.800
you might go berserk.

18:44.340 --> 18:49.080
Thanks for the warning. I'll spar with you another day.

19:02.540 --> 19:03.320
Sir,

19:07.340 --> 19:08.690
um, could you

19:09.020 --> 19:10.450
take me to Chufeng Academy?

19:12.260 --> 19:12.850
Shanhua.

19:21.020 --> 19:21.610
Shanhua.

19:34.340 --> 19:37.450
You really think you can escape?

19:52.820 --> 19:54.370
Gaolu fell seven years ago.

19:55.340 --> 19:57.000
Why is Longming Sanctuary still hunting us down?

19:57.540 --> 19:58.650
Eighteen years ago,

19:59.630 --> 20:02.170
that traitor stayed in Gaolu's palace for several years

20:03.430 --> 20:05.000
and then vanished without a trace.

20:05.580 --> 20:06.170
Tell me!

20:06.580 --> 20:08.130
Where is that traitor hiding?

20:09.500 --> 20:11.170
I don't know what you're talking about.

20:11.630 --> 20:15.040
You'll find out once you get to Longming Sanctuary!

20:54.740 --> 20:55.480
Xiuyuan!

21:36.390 --> 21:38.210
- Shanhua. -Are you okay?

21:41.020 --> 21:41.930
Elder Zhenyun?

21:42.820 --> 21:45.520
Longming Sanctuary is hunting these Gaolu remnants.

21:46.190 --> 21:47.930
Is Xingzheng Hall going to interfere?

21:49.710 --> 21:51.890
You actually got yourselves this beat up by some small fry

21:52.020 --> 21:53.210
from Longming Sanctuary.

21:53.630 --> 21:54.410
What do you mean?

21:57.020 --> 21:58.280
Is Xingzheng Hall

21:58.670 --> 22:00.370
really going against Longming Sanctuary?

22:30.470 --> 22:31.650
His heart meridians are damaged.

22:32.100 --> 22:34.690
Ordinary medicine won't work anymore.

22:39.710 --> 22:41.280
Senior, please save Shanhua.

22:44.500 --> 22:47.320
Gaolu fell seven years ago.

22:48.100 --> 22:49.560
Why are Longming Sanctuary's people

22:49.780 --> 22:51.520
still hunting you?

22:56.300 --> 22:57.370
I dragged Shanhua into this.

22:58.230 --> 23:00.850
It's because... I have a spiritual root.

23:02.060 --> 23:03.480
They won't let me go, fearing I'll become

23:03.820 --> 23:05.850
a threat later.

23:06.910 --> 23:08.080
You are incredibly talented.

23:09.190 --> 23:11.930
You mastered the basic spells Lu Shanhua taught you

23:12.190 --> 23:14.520
and formed your own style.

23:15.740 --> 23:16.480
What a pity.

23:17.580 --> 23:19.450
Xingzheng Hall has made its stance clear.

23:19.820 --> 23:21.370
We won't interfere in Gaolu's affairs.

23:23.540 --> 23:24.720
I'm not asking to join Xingzheng Hall.

23:25.150 --> 23:27.800
I only ask you to save Shanhua.

23:29.260 --> 23:30.610
Shanhua's life is hanging by a thread.

23:31.190 --> 23:32.720
To save him,

23:33.230 --> 23:35.450
we need the power of the nine-tailed fox.

23:37.780 --> 23:38.930
Nine-tailed fox?

23:40.470 --> 23:41.320
What a shame.

23:47.390 --> 23:47.970
Go on.

23:52.670 --> 23:53.410
Her?

23:54.710 --> 23:55.890
Find this tomboy

23:56.150 --> 23:57.970
to track down the nine-tailed fox.

23:58.340 --> 24:00.210
Remember, do not alert anyone else.

24:02.500 --> 24:05.080
Especially the immortal sects.

24:05.280 --> 24:09.080
[Lugong Town]

24:11.540 --> 24:13.450
Little trinkets!

24:13.470 --> 24:15.850
Please take a look. They are for blessings. Really nice.

24:16.390 --> 24:17.520
Wish you many children and great wealth.

24:17.540 --> 24:19.370
The ancestral hall in Lugong Town ahead

24:19.500 --> 24:21.520
is the registration site for Chufeng Academy.

24:21.870 --> 24:23.040
I'll only take you this far.

24:25.260 --> 24:27.080
Mr. Dongyang, you're leaving already?

24:28.390 --> 24:31.210
Then I won't even have anything to remember you by.

24:37.100 --> 24:39.130
Here, take this evil-warding bead bracelet.

24:44.340 --> 24:46.210
Even if you can't get into Chufeng Academy,

24:46.670 --> 24:48.040
with this bracelet,

24:48.710 --> 24:50.650
you should be safe.

24:55.870 --> 24:58.240
Thank you, Mr. Dongyang. You're so kind.

25:03.020 --> 25:04.480
Then why not help me all the way?

25:04.950 --> 25:06.280
Any tips

25:06.630 --> 25:07.800
for getting into Chufeng Academy?

25:07.990 --> 25:09.080
How can I get in smoothly?

25:12.060 --> 25:13.170
I wouldn't know.

25:13.430 --> 25:15.930
Just work hard.

25:17.580 --> 25:20.370
Then... how do you grow that gourd?

25:20.580 --> 25:21.280
Can I grow one?

25:21.430 --> 25:23.210
If I miss you, how do I find you?

25:23.820 --> 25:25.000
You are so good to me.

25:25.020 --> 25:26.370
How can I ever repay you?

25:33.430 --> 25:34.480
Just like Master,

25:34.670 --> 25:35.890
always disappearing into thin air.

25:38.780 --> 25:41.170
Mr. Dongyang, until we meet again!

25:46.950 --> 25:49.000
I'll find Senior Brother first, then look for Master.

25:49.950 --> 25:51.930
Chufeng Academy, here I come!

25:55.950 --> 25:56.720
Make way!

26:07.950 --> 26:09.370
You again, you menace.

26:14.020 --> 26:14.720
What do you want?

26:17.060 --> 26:18.410
I have no money.

26:18.820 --> 26:20.800
As for looks... I've got even less of that!

26:26.870 --> 26:27.930
Where did he hide?

26:28.340 --> 26:30.320
He? Who?

26:31.470 --> 26:32.410
He...

26:33.500 --> 26:34.240
He's in...

26:34.820 --> 26:36.210
He...

26:36.390 --> 26:37.040
He's in...

26:46.820 --> 26:48.370
Trying to mug me?

26:48.950 --> 26:49.800
Come any closer

26:49.950 --> 26:51.280
and I'll gouge your eyes out!

27:01.100 --> 27:02.040
Where's my brother?

27:02.910 --> 27:04.520
Did your assassin accomplices take him?

27:04.780 --> 27:05.210
Tell me!

27:06.190 --> 27:07.800
Wait, are you crazy?

27:08.150 --> 27:09.720
Your brother's missing. Why are you coming after me?

27:10.020 --> 27:11.170
My master's missing too!

27:13.430 --> 27:14.720
You menace.

27:15.470 --> 27:17.170
You showed up out of nowhere in Dongming Town.

27:17.870 --> 27:18.890
And now you've followed me here.

27:19.910 --> 27:21.170
Did you harm my master?

27:21.390 --> 27:22.560
Where did you take him? Tell me!

27:24.950 --> 27:25.970
You're playing the victim.

27:27.230 --> 27:29.280
If those assassins aren't your accomplices,

27:29.820 --> 27:30.930
then you are Wugou's spy.

27:32.340 --> 27:34.210
Wugou's spy? What's that?

27:50.300 --> 27:51.520
I don't have time to waste on you!

28:02.910 --> 28:04.080
Evil-warding beads?

28:12.400 --> 28:15.230
♪If legends tell of a perilous land♪

28:15.230 --> 28:16.690
So many people.

28:16.690 --> 28:18.120
♪Why not give it a shot and march with all our might?♪

28:18.440 --> 28:20.880
♪Fearless through a hundred battles, we finally earn our place♪

28:21.360 --> 28:22.960
♪Happy new semester♪

28:22.960 --> 28:23.710
[Bu Youran, Chufeng Academy]

28:23.710 --> 28:24.280
Here you go.

28:24.950 --> 28:25.610
Thank you.

28:25.950 --> 28:28.520
♪The fierce gale is grasped tightly in our palms♪

28:28.600 --> 28:31.280
♪Hearts united, drawing together for a thunderous strike♪

28:31.440 --> 28:33.520
♪Refusing to coast through life♪

28:33.680 --> 28:36.160
♪Though a crisis is sealed before us, we will not give up♪

28:36.520 --> 28:38.780
♪Leaving our silhouettes between heaven and earth♪

28:38.780 --> 28:39.610
I passed!

28:39.630 --> 28:40.480
Another one went crazy.

28:40.670 --> 28:42.850
Yeah. That's the thirty-seventh one today.

28:42.870 --> 28:43.970
Pass every exam!

28:44.150 --> 28:45.720
Win every battle!

28:45.720 --> 28:46.560
♪We will make all the world's pain kneel before us♪

28:46.920 --> 28:47.780
♪The song of victory never stops♪

28:47.780 --> 28:50.610
Is this how you usually dress?

28:50.610 --> 28:51.920
♪The darkness all turns into illusions♪

28:52.200 --> 28:53.960
♪Unmatched across the Three Realms♪

28:54.470 --> 28:55.320
Your taste

28:56.820 --> 28:58.080
could use some work.

28:59.670 --> 29:00.280
Name?

29:00.670 --> 29:01.280
Hometown?

29:01.500 --> 29:02.760
Which sect are you from?

29:03.260 --> 29:04.370
My name is Xiaobangchui.

29:04.540 --> 29:05.240
I'm from Qingqiu.

29:05.990 --> 29:09.130
Since you are from Qingqiu, do you have a master?

29:09.390 --> 29:12.040
Have you learned any basic spells?

29:12.060 --> 29:12.850
I have a master.

29:13.470 --> 29:15.720
I've learned some talisman drawing.

29:16.470 --> 29:18.850
Talisman drawing is just a minor trick.

29:19.260 --> 29:21.000
Nothing impressive.

29:45.340 --> 29:46.850
[Mr. Li, Elder Zhu, Mr. Cheng, Chufeng Academy]
My hometown suffered a flood.

29:47.150 --> 29:49.890
All my siblings starved to death.

29:51.260 --> 29:52.720
I stole a bun

29:52.870 --> 29:54.280
for my severely ill parents.

29:55.580 --> 29:57.450
But they held my hands tight,

29:57.870 --> 29:59.650
refusing to eat the bun till their last breath

29:59.740 --> 30:00.650
They told me

30:00.670 --> 30:02.450
I had to try my best to get in here,

30:02.950 --> 30:05.280
so I'd never suffer from hunger and cold again.

30:06.390 --> 30:07.040
Only then

30:08.340 --> 30:12.370
can they rest in peace.

30:18.430 --> 30:20.280
Poor child.

30:25.020 --> 30:26.000
Elder Zhu,

30:26.500 --> 30:29.450
should we give her the only special-hardship

30:30.390 --> 30:31.480
exam token?

30:46.100 --> 30:46.760
Hold on.

30:51.540 --> 30:52.560
[Mu, Chufeng Academy]
There is someone here

30:52.870 --> 30:54.000
who might be even worse off.

31:12.300 --> 31:13.760
The fiend.

31:14.430 --> 31:16.610
Why is this menace here too?

31:20.340 --> 31:21.170
Mr. Zuo said

31:21.300 --> 31:23.610
this selection of disciples is special.

31:24.230 --> 31:27.130
So he sent me to assist the three of you.

31:27.820 --> 31:30.280
With you here, we'll have a much easier time.

31:30.300 --> 31:31.690
Come, have a seat.

31:38.340 --> 31:39.610
Do you know this young man?

31:39.990 --> 31:40.800
No.

31:42.230 --> 31:43.410
I just saw him being chased

31:43.870 --> 31:45.650
by some Yue State guards outside the town.

31:46.150 --> 31:47.450
I couldn't stand it,

31:47.670 --> 31:48.800
so I brought him here.

31:50.950 --> 31:52.410
I won't interrupt your discussion.

31:53.060 --> 31:53.610
So I'll just...

31:53.820 --> 31:54.720
No rush.

31:55.230 --> 31:56.040
To be fair,

31:56.100 --> 31:58.000
let's hear what this young man has to say first.

32:06.670 --> 32:07.520
My name is Lei Xiuyuan.

32:08.470 --> 32:10.930
I live in Xigu Village, Luoxia Mountain.

32:11.870 --> 32:14.560
Xigu Village? You're from Xigu Village?

32:18.820 --> 32:19.650
Lei Xiuyuan,

32:20.150 --> 32:22.410
why do you want to apply to Chufeng Academy?

32:38.340 --> 32:39.480
These are the names

32:40.190 --> 32:41.480
of all 161 people in Xigu Village.

32:44.020 --> 32:46.130
My family and villagers

32:47.470 --> 32:49.240
were slaughtered by evil spirits overnight.

32:50.670 --> 32:51.610
I have no skills.

32:52.100 --> 32:54.560
Only by getting into the academy and mastering spells

32:55.630 --> 32:57.410
can I have a chance to avenge them.

32:58.150 --> 33:01.170
He's obviously lying. The masters won't believe him.

33:03.470 --> 33:05.890
Child, stand up.

33:12.950 --> 33:15.280
Five years ago, Xigu Village was struck by a demon disaster.

33:15.710 --> 33:17.970
Several immortal sects sent people to investigate later.

33:18.470 --> 33:19.800
No survivors were found.

33:20.300 --> 33:21.130
Then how did you...?

33:21.990 --> 33:24.890
That night, I was knocked into the river.

33:25.580 --> 33:26.850
My parents shielded me with their bodies.

33:27.470 --> 33:28.720
I hid underwater, not daring to make a sound.

33:29.260 --> 33:30.650
I watched as the whole village was thrown

33:30.950 --> 33:32.970
into the river, one by one.

33:33.230 --> 33:35.080
I am just like those 161 dead people!

33:40.060 --> 33:41.080
I merely survived.

33:41.710 --> 33:44.280
Impressive. He acts even better than me.

33:44.950 --> 33:47.930
Later, I finally found those killers.

33:49.540 --> 33:50.800
They could use spells.

33:52.340 --> 33:55.320
They are disciples of Longming Sanctuary from the Wugou State!

33:59.580 --> 34:01.720
Lei Xiuyuan, do you know

34:02.820 --> 34:06.210
that mortals get severely punished for slandering immortal sects?

34:06.230 --> 34:07.130
Every word I said is true.

34:07.740 --> 34:09.720
This applicant can testify for me.

34:16.430 --> 34:16.970
Come here.

34:20.430 --> 34:20.970
Let go.

34:21.910 --> 34:24.160
That day, I was hiding in a house in Dongming Town

34:24.430 --> 34:25.600
and ran into Xiaobangchui.

34:26.100 --> 34:27.480
The assassins were chasing me.

34:28.220 --> 34:29.890
Thanks to Xiaobangchui's help,

34:30.500 --> 34:31.480
I managed to escape.

34:34.790 --> 34:36.890
So, Xiaobangchui,

34:37.990 --> 34:39.810
is what he said true?

34:43.100 --> 34:43.850
Yes, yes.

34:44.430 --> 34:46.330
Those people were ruthless

34:46.350 --> 34:47.040
and struck to kill.

34:47.350 --> 34:48.770
And they all used spells.

34:57.140 --> 34:58.290
Don't you have a brother?

34:58.750 --> 34:59.450
Where is he?

35:12.220 --> 35:13.600
My brother was a disciple of an immortal sect.

35:14.700 --> 35:15.560
He protected me for years

35:16.750 --> 35:18.810
but got into trouble and was hunted down.

35:19.220 --> 35:20.480
Now he's missing.

35:30.700 --> 35:31.640
The world is vast,

35:33.310 --> 35:34.480
but there's no place for me

35:36.100 --> 35:37.200
unless I get into this academy.

35:43.750 --> 35:44.850
I don't ask for your pity,

35:45.500 --> 35:46.600
only for a chance to take the exam.

35:48.540 --> 35:50.080
I'd be forever grateful.

36:00.990 --> 36:01.930
I never expected

36:02.310 --> 36:03.450
we both have such tragic backgrounds.

36:03.750 --> 36:05.480
But look, I dress worse

36:05.830 --> 36:06.640
and live worse than you.

36:07.100 --> 36:09.200
Plus, I saved your life before.

36:10.830 --> 36:12.970
I'll always remember your kindness in saving me.

36:13.220 --> 36:14.640
I'll repay you someday.

36:14.830 --> 36:16.120
Not "someday". Do it now.

36:17.350 --> 36:18.680
This is all I have.

36:19.140 --> 36:20.730
Hope you don't mind.

36:22.540 --> 36:23.290
If you try to steal my spot again,

36:23.310 --> 36:24.560
I'll skin you alive!

36:24.990 --> 36:27.600
I have a blood debt to settle. Please let me have this.

36:28.500 --> 36:29.450
- I don't want it. - Take it.

36:29.470 --> 36:30.930
No. Don't force it on me.

36:31.660 --> 36:32.480
- No. - Here.

36:32.790 --> 36:34.120
I said no. Let go!

36:49.220 --> 36:50.250
I didn't even know my parents

36:50.270 --> 36:51.850
left me so much money.

36:53.990 --> 36:54.730
I'm leaving.

37:05.990 --> 37:07.080
Master,

37:07.830 --> 37:09.770
it's fine that you abandoned me,

37:10.350 --> 37:12.290
but at least let things go smoothly for me.

37:15.270 --> 37:17.520
Now that jinx stole the exam token.

37:19.060 --> 37:20.480
It cost me so much money to register.

37:32.500 --> 37:33.680
With that evil-warding beads blocking spiritual detection,

37:34.060 --> 37:35.200
I'll just capture her first.

37:43.100 --> 37:44.120
Which loser hit me?

37:57.660 --> 38:01.680
Prince Ying is arriving! Clear the way!

38:07.520 --> 38:09.160
[Zhao Mingli, Zhao Zhijie]

38:09.680 --> 38:10.500
[Lanya]

38:10.500 --> 38:11.640
Prince Ying is giving out money!

38:11.750 --> 38:13.250
Prince Ying is giving out money!

38:13.500 --> 38:14.680
- Let's go! - Prince Ying is giving out money!

38:19.870 --> 38:21.810
So he's the one throwing money around.

38:26.830 --> 38:28.200
A rich mark.

38:51.060 --> 38:52.080
Move! Move!

38:52.100 --> 38:54.120
Make way, people.

38:54.350 --> 38:55.000
Get lost!

38:56.620 --> 38:57.890
Are you okay?

38:57.990 --> 38:59.200
[Baili Gelin]
How can you bully people like that?

38:59.750 --> 39:00.450
Apologize!

39:01.020 --> 39:02.640
Prince Ying and Commandery Princess Lanya are here.

39:03.020 --> 39:04.000
You're nobodies!

39:04.270 --> 39:04.680
Move!

39:04.910 --> 39:06.200
I don't care who you are.

39:06.580 --> 39:07.640
Don't you know how to line up?

39:08.500 --> 39:09.410
You're the nobody!

39:11.310 --> 39:12.160
What did you say?

39:18.520 --> 39:20.280
[Ye Ye]

39:23.830 --> 39:26.680
I've heard Chufeng Academy treats everyone equally.

39:28.830 --> 39:31.410
Whether royalty or commoners,

39:31.700 --> 39:32.600
everyone is treated the same.

39:32.990 --> 39:35.120
What do you think, Prince Ying?

39:36.910 --> 39:38.480
Outrageous! Arrest him!

39:40.700 --> 39:41.560
Don't be rude!

39:45.160 --> 39:49.880
[Ji Tongzhou]

39:54.540 --> 39:55.520
Tongzhou, you're here.

39:57.060 --> 39:58.480
His Majesty sent you to accompany me for the exam,

39:58.870 --> 40:00.250
not to cause trouble.

40:00.500 --> 40:01.970
I wasn't causing trouble.

40:02.430 --> 40:03.930
I was afraid you wouldn't get registered,

40:03.950 --> 40:04.970
so I pushed them aside.

40:05.390 --> 40:06.040
Besides,

40:06.140 --> 40:07.370
what's the point of them registering?

40:07.700 --> 40:08.890
They probably won't get in anyway.

40:09.060 --> 40:10.250
They're just wasting time.

40:10.500 --> 40:11.000
You...

40:11.390 --> 40:13.290
You can't even last one move against my cousin.

40:13.310 --> 40:15.160
How dare you talk big here?

40:16.910 --> 40:17.770
Nonsense!

40:17.950 --> 40:19.680
I just didn't want my whip

40:19.700 --> 40:20.850
to tear your filthy clothes

40:20.870 --> 40:21.680
and offend my eyes!

40:22.470 --> 40:23.520
[Baili Changyue]
I heard the Yue State

40:23.520 --> 40:24.480
values etiquette above all.

40:25.220 --> 40:27.290
After seeing how you conduct yourself today,

40:28.830 --> 40:31.930
it seems the rumors can't be trusted.

40:32.180 --> 40:32.850
How dare you!

40:33.180 --> 40:35.120
You lowlife dare to insult our state?

40:35.180 --> 40:35.890
You're asking for it!

40:36.500 --> 40:37.290
Forget it.

40:37.430 --> 40:39.850
Can't win with words so you're ganging up? Bring it on!

40:39.870 --> 40:40.290
Bring it...

40:40.310 --> 40:41.000
Yeah, bring it on!

40:47.540 --> 40:49.930
Move! Get out of the way!

40:51.310 --> 40:53.680
Seriously, it stinks... back there.

41:00.500 --> 41:01.480
I'm broke

41:01.620 --> 41:02.770
after paying the exam fee.

41:03.700 --> 41:05.600
We'll have to crash here for a few nights.

41:08.660 --> 41:09.520
It's you guys?

41:14.580 --> 41:16.680
Thank you for pushing that manure cart.

41:16.700 --> 41:18.560
That spoiled princess got humiliated.

41:19.140 --> 41:20.560
By the way, what should we call you?

41:21.270 --> 41:23.560
I'm Xiaobangchui. And you three are...?

41:24.750 --> 41:25.520
Xiaobangchui.

41:25.700 --> 41:27.000
I'm Baili Changyue.

41:27.140 --> 41:28.600
This is my sister, Baili Gelin.

41:30.540 --> 41:31.290
I'm Ye Ye.

41:31.430 --> 41:32.930
I'm Gelin and Changyue's cousin.

41:33.540 --> 41:35.520
You're cousins?

41:57.790 --> 41:58.370
Here.

42:09.950 --> 42:11.040
- Slow down. - It's tasty.

42:11.910 --> 42:12.930
So delicious.

42:12.950 --> 42:14.000
It's my cooking, after all.

42:14.020 --> 42:15.450
Haven't had such a good meal in ages.

42:24.180 --> 42:24.850
Who's there?

42:42.050 --> 42:43.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:43.000 --> 42:44.550
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves, the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
